    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:1.3",
          "pli": "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū … pe … bhagavā etadavoca: ",
          "en": "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:1.4",
          "pli": "“bhūtapubbaṃ, bhikkhave, sakko devānamindo sudhammāyaṃ sabhāyaṃ deve tāvatiṃse anunayamāno tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
          "en": "“Once upon a time, mendicants, Sakka, lord of gods, guiding the gods of the Thirty-Three, recited this verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.1",
          "pli": "‘Mā vo kodho ajjhabhavi, ",
          "en": "“Don’t let anger be your master, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.2",
          "pli": "mā ca kujjhittha kujjhataṃ; ",
          "en": "don’t get angry at angry people. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.3",
          "pli": "Akkodho avihiṃsā ca, ",
          "en": "Kindness and harmlessness "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.4",
          "pli": "ariyesu ca paṭipadā; ",
          "en": "are always present in the noble ones. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.5",
          "pli": "Atha pāpajanaṃ kodho, ",
          "en": "For anger crushes bad people "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.6",
          "pli": "pabbatovābhimaddatī’”ti. ",
          "en": "like a mountain.’” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:2.7",
          "pli": "Tatiyo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.1",
          "pli": "Chetvā dubbaṇṇiya māyā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.2",
          "pli": "accayena akodhano; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.3",
          "pli": "Desitaṃ buddhaseṭṭhena, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.4",
          "pli": "idañhi sakkapañcakanti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.5",
          "pli": "Sakkasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. ",
          "en": "The Linked Discourses with Sakka are complete. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:3.6",
          "pli": "Sagāthāvaggo paṭhamo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:4.1",
          "pli": "Devatā devaputto ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:4.2",
          "pli": "rājā māro ca bhikkhunī; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:4.3",
          "pli": "Brahmā brāhmaṇa vaṅgīso, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:4.4",
          "pli": "vanayakkhena vāsavoti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn11.25:4.5",
          "pli": "Sagāthāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi niṭṭhitā. ",
          "en": "The Book With Verses is finished."
        }
      ],
